data.description: This beautiful brick ranch home is located in the perfect spot! Home is located minutes from Somerset and New Lexington. With great features such as the huge concrete driveway, 3 Car attached garages, 4 seasons room, over an acre, new paint, new bathrooms, new flooring, new roof, new windows  and more! This home is move in ready! You will fall in love with the beautiful updates through out the home! Not limited to the kitchen updates, the bathroom updates...the home has updates in each of the  rooms. Outside you will love the huge yard, extensive landscaping and the wonderful town of Somerset! Restaurants, schools, shopping and the freeway are so close yet you are far enough away to enjoy quiet.  You must see this home to fall in LOVE! *
